name: Crosswind! Cathay Pacific Cargo 747-867F [B-LJK] Windy Landing at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Cathay Pacific Cargo made a very late appearance at Calgary International Airport today. The flights are typically operated from 1-5AM, but this bird showed up at 1:55PM, a very welcome sight for the spotters. In addition to that, the pilots had a crosswind of 14 to 19 knots, making for a spectacular touchdown. ATC is included, enjoy!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
